ience%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20flooding%20and%20hurricane%20preparedness%2C%20often%20uses%202D%20images%20and%20renders%20to%20showcase%20new%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20stormwater%20drainage%20systems.%20However%2C%20these%20tools%20failed%20to%20show%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Vitale%20partnered%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.incitu.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInCitu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-augmented-reality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaugmented%20reality%3C%2Fa%3E%20startup%2C%20to%20give%20communities%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20future%20infrastructure%20developments.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20better%20way%20to%20do%20that%20than%20to%20really%20let%20them%20experience%20it%20in%20real%20time%20in%20the%20physical%20space%3F%26quot%3B%20Vitale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInCitu's%20AR%20platform%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20government%20agencies%2C%20real%20estate%20developers%2C%20urban%20planners%2C%20and%20architects%20show%20colleagues%20or%20community%20members%20what%20proposed%20buildings%20and%20infrastructure%20projects%20will%20look%20like%20once%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20communicate%20this%20type%20of%20information%20so%20that%20a%20non-professional%20can%20experience%20it%20as%20they%20walk%20down%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20Dana%20Chermesh-Reshef%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20InCitu%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20InCitu's%20technology%20has%20also%20launched%20in%20seven%20other%20US%20cities%2C%20including%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221677%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dana%20Chermesh-Reshef%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68488ed23d5881a51c1b2514%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221258%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDana%20Chermesh-Reshef%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20InCitu.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dana%20Chermesh-Reshef%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8e20f3b-3441-4a80-ac07-1f0e6f461361%5C%22%3EA%20new%20view%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChermesh-Reshef%20founded%20InCitu%20in%202020%20after%20realizing%20the%20usual%20software%20tools%20used%20to%20present%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20PowerPoint%20presentations%20and%202D%20renders%2C%20struggled%20to%20show%20a%20project's%20full%20scale%20and%20scope%20from%20various%20angles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20a%20project%20in%20an%20environment%20like%20a%20conference%20room%2C%20entirely%20removed%20from%20where%20it%20will%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInCitu's%20smartphone-based%20platform%20tackles%20this%20by%20turning%203D%20models%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcampfire-augmented-virtual-reality-collaboration-platform-collins-aerospace-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAR%20visuals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20people%20see%20a%20project%20as%20it%20would%20appear%20in%20real%20life.%20Instead%20of%20using%20an%20AR%20headset%2C%20users%20can%20scan%20a%20QR%20code%20with%20a%20smartphone%20camera%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20%E2%80%94%20often%20a%20building%2C%20bridge%2C%20roadway%2C%20or%20sidewalk%20%E2%80%94%20to%20view%20the%20life-sized%20AR%20visualization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20download%20any%20app.%20You%20walk%20down%20the%20street%2C%20there's%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20on%20the%20construction%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Chermesh-Reshef%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20use%20their%20smartphones%20to%20walk%20around%20a%20project%20and%20view%20it%20from%20any%20angle%20they%20can%20access.%20InCitu%20also%20supports%20off-site%20viewing%2C%20so%20users%20can%20view%20a%203D%20model%20of%20the%20project%20without%20visiting%20its%20geographical%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInCitu%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridges-to-prosperity-nonprofit-ai-mapping-waterways-rural-communities-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egeospatial%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20draws%20on%20satellite%20and%20street%20view%20imagery%2C%20to%20decide%20where%20an%20imported%203D%20model%20should%20appear%20for%20on-site%20viewing.%20Geospatial%20data%20is%20also%20used%20to%20keep%20the%203D%20model%20in%20the%20right%20location%20as%20a%20user%20moves%20around%20it%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Sarah%20Vitale%20wearing%20a%20green%20shirt%20and%20a%20black%20blazer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849d545f748d8c055f382b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Vitale%20is%20the%20director%20of%20civic%20technology%20at%20the%20TBRPC.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Vitale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22983c5d7d-36d8-4c42-af49-30d0a9202f1f%5C%22%3EUsing%20AR%20to%20visualize%20a%20climate-resilient%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVitale%20encountered%20InCitu%20on%20LinkedIn%20in%20January%202024%20while%20preparing%20for%20TBRPC's%20annual%20regional%20resiliency%20summit.%20This%20two-day%20event%20brings%20together%20roughly%20300%20elected%20officials%2C%20subject%20experts%2C%20and%20residents%20to%20find%20solutions%20for%20the%20region's%20climate%20risks.%20Vitale%20wanted%20a%20way%20to%20give%20attendees%20a%20scaled%2C%20realistic%20visualization%20of%20building%20changes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-investing-green-infrastructure-manage-climate-change-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einfrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20manage%20flood%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitale%20used%20InCitu%20to%20show%20three%20AR%20models%20of%20new%20projects%20during%20on-site%20visits%20near%20the%20event%3A%20a%20house%20elevated%20on%20stilts%20to%20demonstrate%20flood-resistant%20construction%2C%20a%20bioswale%20showing%20natural%20stormwater%20management%2C%20and%20a%20living%20shoreline%20that%20uses%20natural%20materials%20to%20combat%20eroding%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20AR%20visual%20of%20an%20erosion-resistant%20living%20shoreline%20(bioswale)%20using%20natural%20materials%20instead%20of%20concrete%20bulkheads%2C%20next%20to%20the%20original%20photo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849c7a53d5881a51c1b39c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsers%20can%20use%20their%20smartphones%20to%20walk%20around%20a%20project%20and%20view%20it%20from%20any%20angle%20they%20can%20access.%3Cp%3EInCitu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVitale%20said%20that%20her%20organization's%20use%20of%20InCitu%20is%20still%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20phase%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20its%20role%20at%20the%20resiliency%20summit%20was%20in%20part%20to%20let%20attendees%20and%20prospective%20clients%20know%20her%20team%20can%20provide%20AR%20technology%20for%20infrastructure%20planning.%20She%20said%20the%20reception%20so%20far%20has%20been%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20big%2C%20dense%20document.%20It's%20something%20interesting%20that%20people%20can%20engage%20with%20and%20start%20experiencing%20a%20planning%20process%20in%20a%20new%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Vitale%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20AR%20displays%20can%20reduce%20the%20%26quot%3Bengagement%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20accompany%20lengthy%20meetings%20and%20complex%202D%20visualizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology's%20effectiveness%20convinced%20TBRPC%20to%20use%20InCitu%20for%20AR%20demonstrations%20at%20its%202025%20summit%20in%20May.%20The%20organization%20also%20plans%20to%20u