first-year%20investment%20bankers%20for%20jobs%20that%20won't%20start%20for%20two%20years.%20This%20practice%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bon-cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20demands%20junior%20bankers%20compete%20for%20future-dated%20private%20equity%20jobs%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%20after%20being%20notified%2C%20which%20can%20result%20in%20missed%20vacations%20or%20middle-of-the-night%20interviews%20after%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20timeline%20has%20inched%20earlier%2C%20kicking%20off%20before%20candidates%20even%20start%20their%20first%20postgrad%20jobs%20with%20investment%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20comes%20days%20after%20JPMorgan%20told%20its%20incoming%20first-year%20bankers%20that%20they'd%20fire%20anyone%20who%20accepted%20one%20of%20these%20pre-dated%20jobs.%20The%20bank%20also%20sought%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20analysts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruitment-process-has-junior-bankers-freaking-out-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esneaking%20out%20of%20job%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20interview%20with%20private%20equity%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20unethical.%20I%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20and%20I%20may%20eliminate%20it%20regardless%20of%20what%20the%20private-equity%20guys%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-junior-bankers-private-equity-jobs-unethical-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20college%20students%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20first-year%20banker%20planning%20to%20participate%20in%20on-cycle%20recruiting%20said%20he%20was%20stunned%20by%20Apollo's%20letter%20and%20that%20friends%20who%20had%20been%20planning%20to%20interview%20with%20the%20firm%20were%20feeling%20let%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3B