29d9b2a601d01b23e97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAstrology%20has%20been%20popular%20for%20centuries.%3Cp%3EDragonImages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%2C%20I've%20always%20felt%20good%20in%20the%20UK.%20I%20did%20a%20year%20of%20undergrad%20at%20Oxford%20and%20got%20my%20master's%20degree%20in%20London.%20Sure%2C%20it%20probably%20helped%20that%20I%20was%20in%20my%20early%2020s%2C%20and%20my%20only%20life%20responsibilities%20were%20reading%20lists%20and%20pub%20crawls%2C%20but%20I%20was%20happier%20there%20than%20during%20college%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Europe%20looks%20pretty%20good%20for%20me%2C%20too.%20I%20have%20a%20Jupiter%20midheaven%20with%20a%20soulmate%20line%20around%20Belgium%20(that%20explains%20my%20short%20relationship%20with%20a%20Belgian%20violinist%20in%202009).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dom%2C%20I%20could%20%26quot%3Blive%20in%20England%20and%20then%20pop%20around%20and%20travel%20all%20over%20Europe%20and%20just%20be%20peachy%20keen.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20East%20Coast%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichest-neighborhoods-around-new-york-city-2014-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuburbs%20of%20NYC%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20I%20live%20now%2C%20also%20generally%20looked%20pretty%20good%20for%20my%20family%20and%20creative%20lines.%20(If%20I%20ever%20feel%20like%20heading%20up%20to%20the%20Dakotas%2C%20or%20down%20to%20Austin%20or%20Central%20Mexico%2C%20I%20should%20also%20be%20in%20good%20hands.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeward%20and%20Dom%20suggested%20I%20consult%20charts%20for%20my%20whole%20family%2C%20so%20I%20did.%20I%20learned%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband's%20chart%20suggests%20he'll%20feel%20professionally%20drained%20and%20isolated%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20in%20the%20US%2C%20whereas%20his%20UK%20lines%20are%20%26quot%3Bsupportive%20and%20grounding.%26quot%3B%3C%2