re%20just%20aren't%20that%20many%20places%20to%20go%20if%20you%20upset%20a%20studio%20chief%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20all%20of%20the%20above.%20I%20just%20think%20it's%20all%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Also%2C%20the%20ground%20is%20shifting.%20This%20business%20hasn't%20landed%20where%20it's%20going%20to%20land%20yet%2C%20and%20people%20keep%20looking%20backwards%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20just%20need%20to%20get%20moviegoing%20back%20to%20where%20it%20was.%26quot%3B%20That%20boat's%20sailed.%20That's%20not%20gonna%20happen%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we're%20not%20thinking%20about%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20what%20is%20the%20business%20now%3F%20What%20does%20the%20business%20want%20to%20be%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20audience%20is%20trying%20to%20tell%20us%2C%20and%20we're%20not%20listening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20using%20tech%20and%20AI%20in%20your%20work%3F%20There's%20one%20theory%20that%20says%20someone's%20going%20to%20type%20in%20a%20prompt%20and%20the%20AI%20spits%20out%20an%20entire%20movie.%20The%20more%20conservative%20argument%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20improve%20flows%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20using%2010%20visual-effects%20people%2C%20you%20could%20do%20it%20with%20four%20or%20eight.%26quot%3B%20The%20even%20more%20positive%20spin%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20eight%20to%2010%20visual-effects%20people%20could%20do%20much%20better%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20always%20used%20versions%20of%20that.%20If%20it%20wasn't%20proper%20AI%2C%20there%20were%20always%20ways%20to%20shortcut%20those%20kinds%20of%20things%2C%20to%20create%20a%20smoother%20workflow%20and%20all%20of%20that.%20If%20an%20actor%20couldn't%20do%20a%20certain%20stunt%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20put%20their%20face%20on%20something%20else%2C%20that's%20been%20happening%2C%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20get%20easier.%20Which%20is%20scary%20if%20you're%20an%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20bigger%20problem%20is%20not%20making%20stuff%20with%20AI%2C%20but%20deciding%20what%20to%20make%20with%20AI.%20That's%20the%20bigger%20threat%2C%20at%20least%20for%20me%2C%20in%20the%20immediate%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20played%20around%20and%20asked%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20to%20write%20a%20script%20in%20the%20mode%20of%20Scott%20Frank%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah.%20It%20was%20silly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20want%20to%20write%20a%20letter%2C%20a%20business%20letter%20or%20something%20%E2%80%A6%20my%20wife%20needed%20to%20write%20this%20letter%2C%20and%20she%20just%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20see%20what%20ChatGPT%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20sent%20me%20the%20letter%20and%20it%20was%20damn%20good.%20It%20was%20really%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20more%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20algorithm.%20The%20algorithm%20is%20great%20for%20marketing%20after%20something's%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5BBut%5D%20it's%20death%20to%20the%20industry%20to%20use%20it%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20make%20because%20you're%20gaming%20something.%20And%20if%20everybody's%20using%20the%20same%20algorithm%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20snake%20that%20eats%20its%20own%20tail%20eventually.%20That's%20my%20big%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20started%20in%20Hollywood%20the%20old-fashioned%20way%20%E2%80%94%20you%20moved%20there%20and%20spent%20years%20trying%20to%20get%20work%20as%20a%20writer.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wrote%20one%20script%20over%20and%20over%20that%20no%20one%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FLittle_Man_Tate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELittle%20Man%20Tate%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20until%20somebody%20wanted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3