caption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20poor%20internet%20and%20makeshift%20equipment%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20post%20quality%20recipe%20videos.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20her%20first%20pay%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20asked%20my%20family%20members%20to%20stop%20me%20from%20doing%20what%20I%20was%20doing.%20They%20felt%20that%20making%20videos%20or%20being%20on%20social%20media%20is%20culturally%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20quietly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Kaushalya%E2%80%99s%20husband%20has%20always%20been%20supportive%20of%20her%20endeavours.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20only%20knew%20that%20if%20you%20put%20videos%20on%20YouTube%2C%20she%20would%20get%20money%2C%20I%20always%20stood%20by%20her%20and%20the%20decisions%20she%20wanted%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Virendra%2C%20who%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20living%20off%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20power%20of%20language%20and%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Kaushalya%20made%20content%20in%20Hindi%2C%20but%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off.%20The%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20her%20grandmother-in-law%20watched%20a%20video%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20ingredient%20names.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20asked%20me%20what%20turmeric%20and%20red%20chilli%20powder%20are.%20They%20asked%20me%20why%20Dhaniya%20was%20called%20coriander%20in%20my%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Kaushalya%20realised%20%E2%80%94%20millions%20of%20rural%20women%20had%20access%20to%20cheap%20internet%20since%202017%2C%20but%20hardly%20any%20content%20was%20made%20for%20them.%20So%20she%20started%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20in%20Rajasthani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20was%20overwhelming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22aut