%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20started%20flooding%20in%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20India%2C%20from%20Jammu%20to%20Kanyakumari%2C%20Assam%20to%20Gujarat.%20Schools%2C%20army%20personnel%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20juice%20vendors%2C%20and%20people%20from%20every%20walk%20of%20life%20began%20sending%20mango%20seeds.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20season%2C%20he%20had%20received%20more%20than%2011%20lakh%20mango%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20name%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EGutli%3C%2Fem%3E%20Man%E2%80%99%20does%20not%20bother%20me%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20it%20represents%20something%20powerful.%20People%20understand%20the%20cause%2C%20and%20they%20have%20come%20together%20to%20help.%20They%20do%20not%20mock%20me%20anymore%20for%20collecting%20%3Cem%3Egutlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20instead%2C%20they%20try%20to%20help%20out%20in%20whatever%20capacity%20they%20can.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20gutli%20to%20graft%20%E2%80%93%20The%20science%20behind%20the%20saplings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20seeds%20arrive%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20begins%20his%20work.%20The%20seeds%20are%20sorted%2C%20dried%2C%20and%20planted%20in%20raised%20soil%20beds%2C%20as%20mango%20seeds%20need%20minimal%20moisture.%20Germination%20begins%20just%20before%20the%20monsoon%2C%20and%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20seeds%20begin%20to%20sprout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20saplings%20reach%20about%20four%20or%20five%20feet%20tall%2C%20we%20graft%20them%20with%20local%20mango%20varieties%20like%20Langda%20or%20Gulab%20Khas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20guarantees%20that%20the%20trees%20will%20flourish%20in%20their%20environment%20and%20bear%20fruit.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F416806%2Fhow-to-grow-kesar-mango-in-a-pot-steps-to-follow-location-temperature-gujarat-variety%2F%5C%22%20tar